text: <@U05UUKBBC1M> Hey, thank you for responding to my concern. You're right, it says there's a parsing error in the module, but I've thoroughly checked my module code, and there's no parsing error or any missing commas or anything. The code is absolutely fine.

Maybe the error is not in that module specifically but it fails at that particular line. Occasionally using the theme or module check can highlight issues you may have missed (see Marketplace Asset Validation here <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/developer-reference/local-development-cli|https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/developer-reference/local-development-cli>)
